metadata.description:
Dynamic 3D expression, made from a shared common denominator.

Its rudimental shape is the direct derivative of the original wallet address. A 42 character address converted to a series of nodes in time and space that make up this energetic geometric form.

Created to highlight the value of a shared community journey and celebrate the serendipity of it all.
